(144, 'Ferrero Rocher T 16 Gift Box With Personalized Gift Wrapper', 'Chocolates make everything special effortlessly! Be it any occasion chocolates can make the celebrations double in minutes. Here is the best gift that you can present to your loved ones. A Ferrero Rocher T 16 Gift Box with Personalized Gift wrapper with their names on it! Be it birthday, an anniversary of best wishes for an achievement it will be perfect for anything. Adding a personal touch to it will make them feel all the more special. Give this tasty delight to your loved ones and watch a wide smile spread across their face!', 'ferrero_rocher_t_16_gift_box_with_personalized_gift_wrapper_27.09.2017_790538_1.jpg', '790538', '650', '580', '2017-10-04 09:03:07', '182.73.111.', 8, 0),
(145, 'Bournville Cranberry- 80gms With Personalized Diwali Sleeve', 'Lets go desi! This year, send everyone your Diwali greetings with a Bournville Cranberry, and lots of love. Like they say, nothing says love like chocolate! Personalized to your choice, you can now send this delicious chocolate to your loved ones and be remembered as the cool one with the personalized chocolate Diwali wish!', 'bournville_cranberry-_80gms_with_personalized_diwali_sleeve_29.9.17_790293.jpg', '790293', '500', '350', '2017-10-04 09:04:50', '182.73.111.', 8, 0),
(146, 'Cadbury Bournville Cranberry Chocolate - 80 Gm', 'Cadbury brings to you the smooth, fine and intense experience of the Bournville Dark chocolate. Cadbury takes the best cocoa beans sourced from Ghana, roasts and grinds them with utmost care to supplement each bar of Bournville with its characteristic bittersweet taste. Bite into this unique thin slab of chocolate and let its intense flavour notes gradually evolve on your palate. Moreover, being rich in cocoa (a natural source of anit-oxidants), Cabdury Bournville is good for your overall metabolism. Do you have a friend who is worried about calories and is extremely fitness concious? This chocolate is the perfect gift for her! Its luscious cranberry taste adds to the overall flavour of this delectable treat!', 'ck.JPG', '729637', '120', '100', '2017-10-04 09:07:19', '182.73.111.', 8, 0),
